pidgin-indicator: Ubuntu Indicator Plugin for Pidgin
====================================================

1.0.2 (2024-12-02):

* Support gcc-14
* Support ayanta-appindicators

1.0.1 (2018-05-02):

* Reduce logging spam.
* Update README.
* Bring debian build files into the tree.

1.0 (2016-05-18):

* Add Russian translation.
* Add Spanish translation.
* Add links to package repositories.

0.9 (2015-02-06):

* Implemented proper blinking notification for status icon.
* Added Simplied Chinese translation.

0.8 (2014-09-20):
-----------------

* Added Hungarian translation.

0.7 (2014-02-04):
-----------------

* Improved handling of status icon state
* Menu is now rebuilt when Plugin Actions change

0.6 (2014-01-27):
-----------------

* Fixed focusing of conversation tabs when going to
  unread conversations.
* Enabled translations.

0.5 (2014-01-19):
-----------------

Initial release.

Fully functional, with one exception:
* Plugin Action menu items are not refreshed.
  You must restart pidgin or reload the plugin
  to update these menu items.
